                <h2>Colour Attributes</h2>
    
                <p>
                Click the icon (XPath = <span class="xpath">div[@id='colour-picker']//a</span>) to open 
                the colour picker.
                <p>
                Each coloured square on picker has a <i>rel</i> attribute with 
                the hex value of the colour e.g. <span class="xpath">//a[@rel='38fff8']</span>.
                <p>
                The large coloured block will have a css style with <i>background-color</i> equal to the 
                selected colour i.e. <span class="xpath">style="background-color:#38fff8;"</span> selected with
                <span class="xpath">//div[@id='colour-block']/@style</span>.
    
